body: So, this is kind of a fun, and ridiculous game, but try to type the name of the player above you with your chin! (Smaller people have an advantage for once!). For example, here's me trying to type my own name with my chin: szl;aftyesmjrxc.... Yeah, that was a fail. If you just can't even do it, try it with your nose!
